Sahi choice — anime app visually 🔥 banega.

Main tujhe best + free + no headache APIs de raha hoon:

🎯 1. BEST API (use this)
👉 Jikan API
Base URL:
https://api.jikan.moe/v4
🔍 Example endpoints
🔹 Search anime
https://api.jikan.moe/v4/anime?q=naruto
🔹 Top anime (homepage ke liye 🔥)
https://api.jikan.moe/v4/top/anime
🔹 Anime details
https://api.jikan.moe/v4/anime/{id}
🔹 Pagination (IMPORTANT)
https://api.jikan.moe/v4/anime?q=naruto&page=2

👉 Ye tere liye perfect hai:

debounce → search
pagination → page param
UI → images already milti hain
🚀 2. Alternate (optional)
👉 AniList API

👉 Thoda complex hai (GraphQL)
👉 beginner ke liye avoid kar abhi

🧠 Simple plan (follow this)
Day 1:
top anime fetch
cards me show
Day 2:
search + debounce
Day 3:
pagination
Day 4:
details page
💀 Important warning

👉 Jikan API:

rate limit hai (zyada fast calls → error)

👉 Tera debounce yaha kaam aayega 😏

🎯 Final

👉 Start with:

https://api.jikan.moe/v4/top/anime

👉 Phir:

search
pagination
details
